where use list:
______________
1. Go to SE11 --> provide table name- VBAK --> click on where used list --> deselect all ---> now select the data definitions --> click on ok.
   Here you can able to see all the data definitions, that has been created on top of this CDS view.

   main disadvantages : some of the cds views are not show over here.

